@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Extend Workflow Engine

' Text Description:
' 1. The System Administrator submits a new Step Type component.
' 2. The system performs a validation check for interface compliance.
' 3. If the component is compliant, it is registered in the Extension Registry.
' 4. The engine refreshes its internal component cache to include the new type.
' 5. If validation fails, an error message is displayed to the Administrator.

start
:Submit new Step Type component;
:Validate interface compliance;
if (Compliant?) then (yes)
  :Register in Extension Registry;
  :Refresh component cache;
  :Display Success;
else (no)
  :Display Validation Error;
endif
stop
@enduml